&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.libertycars.gr&quot;&gt;Check it out&lt;/a&gt; here.&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>LefterisTatakis</name></author><category term="project" /><category term="ecommerce, lambdas, AWS, Angular, JavaScript, Nodejs" /><summary type="html">What did I build it with</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Cretecompare</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/cretecompare/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Cretecompare" /><published>2018-01-23T22:10:00+00:00</published><updated>2018-01-23T22:10:00+00:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/cretecompare</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/cretecompare/">&lt;p&gt;Overview of the key outcomes of this project:&lt;/p&gt;
